These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the paramedic is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Job   | accountant | paramedic | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, alhambra, vegafina
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Cigar   | prince | vegafina | alhambra |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Pet   | horse | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Sport   | volleyball | surfing | weightlifting |

