.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, pall-mall, game
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
2. the game-smoker is between the pall-mall-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | game | baccarat |

